title: Isaac Asimov's Science Fiction Magazine collection UPDATE-1
description:
This first update to my previous Asimov torrent brings seven more magazines, courtesy of a nice gentleman from Argentina that wished to remain anonymous. Now the volumes 35 and 35 are complete. Thanks, hermano!


Asimov's Science Fiction v34n08 (Aug 2010)

Asimov's Science Fiction v35n01 (Jan 2011)

Asimov's Science Fiction v35n02 (Feb 2011)

Asimov's Science Fiction v35n04-05 (Apr-May 2011)

Asimov's Science Fiction v35n08 (Aug 2011)

Asimov's Science Fiction v37n02 (Feb 2013)

Asimov's Science Fiction v37n10-11 (Out-Nov 2013)
